comCesExtension.description: This is the Zhone module identifier for the Zhone CES MIB extension module.

zhoneAtmfCESConfExtTable.name: zhoneAtmfCESConfExtTable
zhoneAtmfCESConfExtTable.description: Zhone extension table for the atmfCesConfTable defined in atmfCES.

zhoneAtmfCESConfExtEntry.name: zhoneAtmfCESConfExtEntry
zhoneAtmfCESConfExtEntry.description: Zhone extension entry for the atmfCesConfEntry defined in atmfCES.

zhoneAtmfCESDs0Bundle.name: zhoneAtmfCESDs0Bundle
zhoneAtmfCESDs0Bundle.description: This value is a bit field indicating the ds0's in the ds0 bundles.

zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESSrcIpAddr.name: zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESSrcIpAddr
zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESSrcIpAddr.description: The local IP address associated with the ces DS0 bundle, which must have an associated floating IP adress configured on the UPLINK.

zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESDstIpAddr.name: zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESDstIpAddr
zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESDstIpAddr.description: The far end IP address destination for the ces DS0 Bundle The local UPLINK must know how to route to the far end IP address.

zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESSrcPort.name: zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESSrcPort
zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESSrcPort.description: The local UDP port associated with the ces DS0 Bundle.

zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESDstPort.name: zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESDstPort
zhoneAtmfCESConfExtAtmfCESDstPort.description: The far end UDP port destination for the CES DS0 Bundle.

zhoneAtmfCESGroup.name: zhoneAtmfCESGroup
zhoneAtmfCESGroup.description: A collection of object from zhoneAtmfCESConfExtTable
